## 📊 Project Overview

Comprehensive statistical analysis of software defects using:
- Multiple Linear Regression (defect prediction)
- One-Way ANOVA (methodology comparison)
- Logistic Regression (high-risk classification)
- Bootstrap & Permutation (robustness validation)

**Dataset:** NASA-like software metrics (10,885 modules)  
**Goal:** 100/100 on final project

---

## 🚀 QUICK START (3 Commands)

```r
# 1. Generate NASA-like data (5 seconds)
source("GENERATE_NASA_DATA.R")

# 2. Run scripts individually OR use master script
source("01_data_preparation.R")
source("02_exploratory_analysis.R")
source("03_multiple_regression.R")
source("04_anova.R")
source("05_logistic_regression.R")
source("06_bootstrap_permutation.R")

# 3. Check outputs/
list.files("outputs/figures")  # Should have 11 figures
list.files("outputs/tables")   # Should have 8-10 tables
```

