## 📊 Outputs Explained

### Figures (All saved as PDF + high-res PNG):

| Figure | Description | Use in Report |
|--------|-------------|---------------|
| Fig1 | Defect distributions (original vs log) | Introduction/Data section |
| Fig2 | Correlation heatmap | Regression section |
| Fig3 | Scatterplots (defects vs predictors) | Regression section |
| Fig4 | Boxplot by methodology | ANOVA section |
| Fig5 | Density by risk level | Logistic section |
| Fig6 | Risk rate by methodology | Logistic section |
| Fig7 | Regression diagnostics (4-panel) | Regression assumptions |
| Fig8 | Violin plot by methodology | ANOVA section |
| Fig9 | ROC curve | Logistic performance |
| Fig10 | Bootstrap distributions | Bootstrap section |
| Fig11 | Permutation null distribution | Permutation section |

### Tables (All CSV format):

- `descriptive_statistics.csv` - Mean, SD, Min, Max for all variables
- `correlation_matrix.csv` - Pearson correlations
- `regression_coefficients.csv` - β values, p-values, CIs
- `regression_vif.csv` - Multicollinearity check
- `anova_descriptive.csv` - Mean defects by methodology
- `anova_tukey.csv` - Pairwise comparisons
- `logistic_odds_ratios.csv` - OR values with CIs
- `bootstrap_cis.csv` - Bootstrap confidence intervals
- `permutation_results.csv` - Permutation test results

