- Waterfall Mean = [value]
- Hybrid Mean = [value]
- Mean Difference = [value]
- η² = [value]

### From Script 5 (Logistic):
- Odds Ratios for each predictor
- AUC = [value]
- Accuracy = [%]
- Sensitivity = [%]
- Specificity = [%]

### From Script 6 (Bootstrap):
