## 📈 Expected Results (Approximate)

Based on simulated NASA-like data:

- **Regression:** R² ≈ 0.60-0.70
- **ANOVA:** F ≈ 40-60, p < 0.001, η² ≈ 0.10-0.15
- **Logistic:** AUC ≈ 0.85-0.90, Accuracy ≈ 80-85%
- **Bootstrap:** CIs will not overlap (confirming difference)

Your actual values will vary slightly based on random seed.

